 <span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_65023839" title="Flag this comment as Inappropriate" class="ui-icon flag fright" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23555325&amp;op=flag&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=65023839" onclick="return false;">Flag as Inappropriate</a>
